# MovieList — navigation and screens

## Types

- All route params and navigator param lists live in **`src/navigation/types.ts`**. Import param types from there — no stringly-typed routes.

## Stack per tab

- **Nested stack per tab** for tab-only routes (each tab’s main + light stack). **`Detail`** and **`SeeAll`** live on the **root stack only** (siblings of `MainTabs`) so the tab bar never appears on those screens; **back** returns to `MainTabs` with the active tab unchanged.

## Params

- Pass **ids** (e.g. **`movieId: number`**) — **not** full movie objects — through navigation params. Hydrate detail via hooks using the id.

## Screens vs data

- **`src/screens/**`** compose layout and wire hooks. **No** direct TMDB or **`movies.ts`** calls from screen files — only hooks under **`src/hooks/`**.
